/*
NAME: cleanPRIO.do
USING .dta file(s): prio_original.dta
USING .do file(s): none

DESCRIPTION: Cleans PRIO data.  Codes new variables that capture the number of wars, type of war, and intensity of war for each location-year.
 
NOTE: internationalized civil conflict counted as both civil conflict AND interstate conflict 
 
AUTHOR: Joe Wright
ORIGIN DATE: 1.9.15
LAST UPDATE: 1.9.15
*/
/* episodes that are still ongoing in December 2013 */
/* extrasystemic, interstate, or internationalized civil conflict */

varlist.value: "Civil conflict intensity: 1=<1000 deaths; 2=>1000 deaths (max for all conflicts in location-year) (PRIO)"
"Int'l conflict intensity: 1=<1000 deaths; 2=>1000 deaths (max for all conflicts in location-year) (PRIO)"
"Duration of international conflict: duration of longest lasting conflict up to year t (PRIO)"
"Duration of civil conflict: duration of longest lasting conflict up to year t (PRIO)"
"Cumulative civil conflict intensity: 0=<1000 deaths; 1=>1000 deaths (max across all conflicts in location-year (PRIO)"
"Cumulative int'l conflict intensity: 0=<1000 deaths; 1=>1000 deaths (max across all conflicts in location-year (PRIO)"

=.value: "int_intra int_inter intra inter duration_intra duration_inter cumint_intra cumint_inter"

value: /* assume no conflict if not listed, except for 1946 */

varlist.value: "Lagged civil conflict intensity: 1=<1000 deaths; 2=>1000 deaths (max for all conflicts in location-year) (PRIO)"
"Lagged int'l conflict intensity: 1=<1000 deaths; 2=>1000 deaths (max for all conflicts in location-year) (PRIO)"
"Lagged duration of international conflict: duration of longest lasting conflict up to year t (PRIO)"
"Lagged duration of civil conflict: duration of longest lasting conflict up to year t (PRIO)"
"Lagged cumulative civil intensity: 0=<1000 deaths; 1=>1000 deaths (max across all conflicts in location-year (PRIO)"
"Lagged cumulative int'l intensity: 0=<1000 deaths; 1=>1000 deaths (max across all conflicts in location-year (PRIO)"
